    {A : Set X}
    (h : closure (A : Set X) = interior (closure (A : Set X))) :
    IsOpen (closure (A : Set X)) := by
  have hOpen : IsOpen (interior (closure (A : Set X))) := isOpen_interior
  simpa [h] using hOpen
